Gnowsys works as single networked database that links a vast spectrum of knowledge from fields and are made easily accessible to one and all. Gnowsys stores a huge knowledge base that consists of Semantics & relationships among this data is added to the knowledge base using the logic of propositions created using subjects & predicates all in the form of Ontologies.   
	The Gnowsys Servers when connected across a Distributed Network will require a system that will facilitate the Knowledge in Gnowsys Servers to be accessible and shareable via the Internet. The MozGnowser Mozilla Firefox Extension will enable knowledge in the Gnowsys database to be accessed by users and shared via internet. It will provide a user friendly interface to search and manipulate data on the Gnowsys Server. 



INSTALLATION 

Please install the required dependency of PyXPCOMext from the following link according to the Mozilla browser version and the Operating system in use 
http://pyxpcomext.mozdev.org/downloads.html

Please drag the MozGnowser.xpi onto the browser or use the File > Open File > <path to the XPI file> from the browser window

Make sure to have Registered on the Gnowsys Website that you are trying to login from MozGnowser



the main python component is in the folder  gnowmoz@gnowledge.org/components/gnowmoz.py

the main JS component is in the folder gnowmoz@gnowledge.org/chrome/gnowmoz/content/js/gnowmoz.js